Rick Tanner 2025-05-28

Add four new cursed cloaks to add variety to the
cursed item selection for cloaks.
- cloak of the Inferno, which attunes the wearer to
    fire, but also makes them vulnerable to fire damage
- cloak of Freezing, which is the same for ice
- cloak of Conductivity, which is the same for electricity
- cloak of Anchoring, which denies access to Teleportation spells.
